==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Necessitous
<hw>Ne*ces"si*tous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>n⟦eacute⟧cessiteux</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Very needy or
indigent; pressed with poverty.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Necessitous</qex> heirs and penurious parents.</q>
<rj><qau>Arbuthnot.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Narrow; destitute; pinching; pinched; <as>as,
<ex>necessitous</ex> circumstances</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Ne*ces"si*tous*ly</wf>, adv. --
<wf>Ne*ces"si*tous*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Necessitude</ent>⟦br⟧
